name: ABBYSON_LIVING_Newport_Outdoor_Espresso_Brown_Wicker_4-piece_Conversation_Set
reviews: Arrived on time, fairly easy to assemble other than having to use a mallet to make some of the holes line up. Downside is that this is really small, I wish I'd paid attention to the dimensions. It works though and looks good in the space, just not deep seat furniture I'd wanted.
I love this set, it looks beautiful on my deck. One thing to keep in mind is that the backs are low, it would have been nice if they had been a little higher but I still love it.
Very uncomfortable, pieces hard to put together and don't fit well. Don't buy this one.
description:
Bring indoor comfort to your exterior living space with this outdoor wicker conversation set with coordinating cushions. Crafted from PE wicker to give you all of wicker's beauty without its maintenance requirements, this outdoor wicker conversation set offers seating for four, making it ideal for intimate get-togethers on the deck or by the pool.
Sturdy constructionNeutral colors to match any decorPerfect for poolside, your deck, or backyard spaceSet includes: One (1) loveseat, two (2) armchairs, one (1) coffee tableMaterials: PE wicker, powder-aluminum frame, water-resistant cushionsUpholstery color: Espresso brown wicker with beige cushionLoveseat dimensions: 33.5 inches high x 45 inches wide x 25 inches deepArmchair dimensions: 33.5 inches high x 24 inches wide x 25 inches deepCoffee table dimensions: 19.5 inches high x 35.5 inches wide x 19.5 inches deepMaterialAluminum, WickerChair TypeSetsChair Back HeightStandardColorBrownProduct FeaturesCushion Included
